parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Fault Code P12A6 and ECM Software Issue
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine fault code P12A6 can cause the vehicle to not start, leaving the driver stranded, and potentially lead to accidents or other electrical problems.
symptoms: instrumentation is erratic and not reading properly on the instrument cluster
and the engine fault code P12A6 is displayed.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Battery Failure and Hydrogen Sulfide Gas Leak
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger-side battery can cause hydrogen sulfide gas to leak into the passenger compartment, compromising the safety of the occupants and potentially leading to health issues.
symptoms: and headaches and nausea in occupants

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Infotainment System and Center Instrument Cluster Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system and center instrument cluster can cause the driver to lose critical information, potentially leading to accidents or other safety issues.
symptoms: The infotainment system and center instrument cluster go completely black
and the system may randomly come back to life.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Computer Malfunction and Trailer Brake Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The computer malfunction can cause the trailer brakes to fail, potentially leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: reducing power and taking away trailer brakes
and the vehicle may shut off.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Progressive Pause Start and Battery Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The progressive pause start can cause the vehicle to not start, leaving the driver stranded, and potentially lead to accidents or other electrical problems.
symptoms: The vehicle has a pause start
it will not start at all
with no power and unable to turn off the park brake.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission valve body can cause the rear tires to lock up, leading to loss of control, skidding, and potential accidents, which can be deadly.
symptoms: exterior and undercarriage of the vehicle covered with transmission fluid.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission fluid line can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to loss of acceleration, and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: exterior and undercarriage of the vehicle covered with transmission fluid

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The exhaust system heat issue can cause damage to the item being towed, such as melting trim, and potentially leading to a fire hazard.
symptoms: Extreme heat building on the item being towed

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The computer system failure can cause the vehicle to reduce power, take the trailer brakes off-line, and shift gears erratically, leading to potential accidents and loss of control.
symptoms: Computer lights up on the dash

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Tread Separation and Tire Failure on Goodyear Wrangler Trail Runner AT Tires
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected tread separation and tire failure can cause loss of control, accidents, and damage to the vehicle, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
